  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下零售系统的整体架构。客户端这边有四个主要模块：收银台POS系统、订单管理、优惠券系统，还有一个重复的优惠券节点我后面会解释。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "Cliente"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我注意到C3和C4都是Retail_CouponSystem，这是有意为之的吗？另外Vite子图里的P1是客户忠诚度系统对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "P1",
        "Vite"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，C3和C4确实是同一个系统的两个实例，分别处理不同的优惠券逻辑。P1是客户忠诚度模块，放在Vite子图里是因为它是前端运行时的一部分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "P1",
        "Vite"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "明白了。那服务端我规划五个节点：S1和S2都是优惠券系统，S3和S4都是订单管理，S5是库存系统。这样分配合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "Servidor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，S1和S2是优惠券的主备或者分片实例，S3处理订单创建，S4处理订单查询，S5是核心库存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，三个子图Cliente、Vite、Servidor已经画好了。现在来连主线：C1到C2，然后到P1，再到S1，这样串起来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，C1到C2是双向还是单向？实际场景是POS机发起订单，订单系统可能回调POS，但主流程是C1→C2。P1是忠诚度计算，插在中间没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我先用单向连线。继续服务端：S1→S2→S3→S5这条主链路，同时S2还要分叉到S4，最后S4也连到S5。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务端链路没问题。但还有一条关键回线：S5处理完库存后，要把结果通过JSON格式返回给C3，这个JSON要包含控制台日志、错误信息、符号表和AST。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3",
        "JSON"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "AST也返回给前端？这是调试用途还是运行时需要的？另外C3收到后还要传给C4对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "AST"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这个设计比较特殊，C3是优惠券解析器，C4是优惠券执行器，AST是给C4用的。调试信息回传是为了前端能直接展示执行状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "AST"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，S5到C3的连线我标注上\"JSON con consola, errores, símbolos, AST\"。C3到C4也连上。整体结构差不多了，你检查一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现C4的标注有问题——它现在显示的还是Retail_CouponSystem，但实际上应该是Retail_CouponExecutor之类的，不过先保持和代码一致吧。另外S2到S4的连线方向确认是S2→S4吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C4",
        "S2",
        "S4"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我查一下，S2是优惠券系统的第二个实例，S4是订单查询。业务上是优惠券验证通过后创建订单查询，所以S2→S4是对的。C4的名称我按你给的保留Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S2",
        "S4",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。再确认一下P1的位置——它虽然在Vite子图里，但逻辑上属于客户端 Loyalty 层，和C1-C2-C3-C4是平级调用关系，不是从属。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "Vite",
        "C1",
        "C2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整视觉层级。现在所有连线：C1-C2-P1-S1，然后S1-S2-S3-S5，S2-S4-S5，S5回连C3，C3-C4。还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
